    public static class Mainline.Key.ObjectRef
extends Mainline.Key.BoneRef
implements java.lang.Comparable<Mainline.Key.ObjectRef>
    Represents an object reference in a Spriter SCML file. An object reference extends a Mainline.Key.BoneRef with a zIndex, which indicates when the object has to be drawn.
